Running command: python - <<'PY'
import requests
# maybe there is /datasets endpoint but requires query params
for url in [
    'https://api.cellxgene.cziscience.com/dp/v1/dataset',
    'https://api.cellxgene.cziscience.com/dp/v1/datasets/',
    'https://api.cellxgene.cziscience.com/dp/v1/datasets?limit=1',
    'https://api.cellxgene.cziscience.com/dp/v1/datasets?dataset_id=21d3e683-80a4-4d9b-bc89-ebb2df513dde',
    'https://api.cellxgene.cziscience.com/dp/v1/datasets?where=dataset_id:21d3e683-80a4-4d9b-bc89-ebb2df513dde',
]:
    try:
        r=requests.get(url, timeout=10)
        print(url, r.status_code, r.headers.get('content-type'))
        print(r.text[:200])
    except Exception as e:
        print(url, 'error', e)
